.PP
RFC4506 defines \f[CR]bool\f[R] in XDR source as equivalent to an
\f[CR]enum\f[R] with name identifiers \f[CR]TRUE\f[R] and
\f[CR]FALSE\f[R].
goxdr translates XDR\[cq]s \f[CR]bool\f[R] to go\[cq]s native
\f[CR]bool\f[R] type.
